transcript:

Executive: Kiski kya? India Mart se baat kar raha hu. Meri baat nahi. Sushil ji Sushil ji Mishra ji alag hai, mai Dilshad hu abhi.
Customer: Mishra ji ka number call kijiye. Haan ji, haan ji.
summary:

- Executive offered to call Mishra.
